*   [Trump National Doral Miami](/Trump_National_Doral_Miami): An 800-acre resort with five courses, 700 hotel rooms, and extensive amenities. Trump acquired the property out of bankruptcy for $150 million in 2012 and invested over $250 million in renovations. Its value was estimated at over $1 billion, with a $125 million mortgage in 2013.
