##### International

*   Trump International Golf Club, Dubai: Managed by the Trump Organization and owned by [Damac Properties](/Damac_Properties), this course opened in 2017. Trump's association with Damac chairman [Hussain Sajwani](/Hussain_Sajwani) has been cited as a potential conflict of interest.
